<li>Members
<ul>
<li>Space allocation
<ul>
<li>We rely on members' honour to keep to their membership privilege tier</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>"Corporate" members
<ul>
<li>People join as individuals, not as part of companies, and are hence subjected to the same community policy as everyone else.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Fees
<ul>
<li>Trial members only get one trial
<ul>
<li>They are unable to subscribe to a trial membership again once they stop their existing trial membership. e.g. trial, stop, trial.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Paypal will charge a fee either way if you pay via credit card
<ul>
<li>Make it clear on the wiki</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Otherwise, let's use bank transfer as the most convenient way forward
<ul>
<li>Individual banks might charge exchange/transactional fee. Members to verify this on their own.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
